lead_paragraph: James Milner has backed fellow England midfielder Dele Alli to continue his meteoric rise but urged the media not to put too much pressure on the teenager as it could have a detrimental affect on his development.

headline.print_headline: Milner Backs Alli to Thrive Despite Media Pressure
headline.main: Milner Backs Alli to Thrive Despite Media Pressure
